iederung und in verständlicher Sprache die jeweiligen Werke vor und zeigen ihre Relevanz für die heutigen und zukünftigen Kulturwissenschaften. Ein unverzichtbares Hilfsmittel für Studium und Lehre in den Kulturwissenschaften.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aCultural Studies. 4aEinführung. 4aKultur. 4aKulturphilosophie. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural Theory.  aCulture.  aIntroduction.  aPhilosophy of Culture.  aSociology of Culture.1 aAdloff, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAhaus, Björn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBarboza, Amalia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeer, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonacker, Thorsten, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBöhm, Roswitha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChrist, Michaela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDelitz, Heike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDrechsel, Benjamin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDüring, Marten, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEntzian, Annett, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aErll, Astrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFischer, Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFitzner, Gunnar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFlender, Armin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrank, Susi K., econtributor.4ctb